name: Small Personalised Jute Bag
description:
Approx 20x15cm.
Embellished and designed to your own unique specifications.

Once payment is made Please e-mail  kate@helter-skelter.org.uk and include below order form;
 

 Hair Colour:
 Eye Colour:
 Dress Colour/theme: 
Name printed on bag:
Paypal email:
Postal Address:
 
Additional Information: [Please include any further information about your bag. This can be your favourite colours , hobbies and personality traits.]
 

 

 
Please note these bags and gifts are handmade and extra care must be given when handled. These bags and gifts are not waterproof therefore please be vigilant. I will not be held liable for any wear and tear therefore if you do have any issues with your order please contact me within 48 hours of receiving it. Postage and packaging price is not included in the product price and will be decided at time of purchase. As these gifts are personalised they cannot be fully refunded after 48 hours of receiving the order form.
